text.div:
This value set includes codes based on the following rules:

  • Include all codes defined in http://www.ama-assn.org/go/cpt
  • Include all codes defined in http://www.cms.gov/Medicare/Coding/HCPCSReleaseCodeSets
  • Include all codes defined in https://www.cms.gov/Medicare/Medicare-Fee-for-Service-Payment/ProspMedicareFeeSvcPmtGen/HIPPSCodes
  • Include all codes defined in http://hl7.org/fhir/us/davinci-pct/CodeSystem/PCTGFEItemProcedureCodes
